---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Age Calculator" description="Privacy policy for the Age Calculator. All calculations run 100% locally in your browser. No data is collected, stored, or transmitted.">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <!-- Simple Nav Header -->
    <header class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full bg-canvas/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-hairline shadow-level-1 min-h-14 md:min-h-16 transition-all">
      <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-3 md:px-6 py-2 md:py-0 flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-1.5 focus-ring rounded-sm py-1 shrink-0">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-mute">0.0.1</span>
          <span class="font-sans font-semibold text-sm md:text-lg tracking-tight select-none text-ink leading-tight">AGE CALCULATOR.</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/"
          class="px-3 py-1.5 bg-canvas hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink border border-hairline rounded-sm font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider focus-ring transition cursor-pointer"
        >← Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="flex-1 w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 py-12 md:py-20">
      <article class="prose prose-sm md:prose-base max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-mute font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-8">Last updated: June 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-6 text-body text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Your Privacy Matters</h2>
            <p>This tool is designed with privacy as a core principle. Below is what you can expect when you use the Age Calculator.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="bg-canvas border border-hairline rounded-lg p-5 md:p-6">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-link shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">All calculations run locally</strong>
                  <span class="text-body text-sm">Every age calculation happens directly in your browser. No server requests are made.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-link shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">No birth dates are stored</strong>
                  <span class="text-body text-sm">Your birth date is never saved on any server. It exists only in your browser's local storage for convenience and can be cleared at any time.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-link shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">No accounts required</strong>
                  <span class="text-body text-sm">There is no sign-up, login, or user registration. Just open the page and use the tool.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-link shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">No personal information collected</strong>
                  <span class="text-body text-sm">We do not collect, track, or store any personally identifiable information (PII).</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-link shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">No data transmitted</strong>
                  <span class="text-body text-sm">Your age data never leaves your device. No analytics, no telemetry, no external API calls.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-link shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-sm">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-ink font-semibold block">Data never leaves your device</strong>
                  <span class="text-body text-sm">Everything you enter stays on your computer or phone. Close the tab and it is gone.</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p>This site uses Google Fonts (Inter and JetBrains Mono) for typography. No other third-party scripts, trackers, or services are loaded. No cookies are set by this application.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>If this privacy policy changes, the "Last updated" date at the top will reflect the revision. Continued use of the tool after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
          </section>

          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-hairline">
            <a href="/"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2.5 bg-primary hover:bg-neutral-800 text-on-primary rounded-sm font-sans font-medium text-sm focus-ring transition shadow-level-2"
            >← Back to Age Calculator</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
